name: Jungle Cruise
Description: Chart a course for high adventure on a scenic and comedic boat tour of exotic rivers across Asia, Africa and South America.

name: Pirates of the Caribbean
Description: Set sail on a swashbuckling voyage to a long-forgotten time and place when pirates and privateers ruled the seas.

name: The Magic Carpets of Aladdin
Description: Fly high over Adventureland on an enchanted carpet ride inspired by the Disney movie Aladdin.

name: Walt Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room
Description: Tropical birds, Tiki gods and colorful flowers come to life in a swinging South Seas musical extravaganza.

name: "it's a small world"
Description: Embark on a whimsical boat ride past a jubilant chorus of children from around the globe.

name: Dumbo the Flying Elephant
Description: Soar high in the sky—and see an elephant fly—on a whimsical flight aboard Dumbo.

name: Mad Tea Party
Description: Spin ‘round and ‘round in a giant teacup during a madcap music-filled whirlwind.

name: Meet Cinderella and a Visiting Princess at Princess Fairytale Hall
Description: Cinderella is waiting to welcome you to the place where a dream is a wish your heart makes.

name: Meet Princess Tiana and a Visiting Princess at Princess Fairytale Hall
Description: Dig a little deeper during an enchanted encounter with Princess Tiana.

name: Mickey's PhilharMagic
Description: Disney magic meets Disney music in this spectacular 12-minute, 3D fantasy adventure starring Donald Duck.

name: Peter Pan's Flight
Description: Embark on a high-flying adventure over iconic scenes made famous in Disney’s animated film.

name: Prince Charming Regal Carrousel
Description: Ride atop a regal steed and gallop through a whirling backdrop of wondrous color and whimsical music.

name: Seven Dwarfs Mine Train
Description: Race through the diamond mine from Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs on a swaying family coaster ride.

name: The Barnstormer
Description: Take flight above Storybook Circus with Goofy in a homemade stunt airplane for a thrilling junior roller coaster ride.

name: The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh
Description: Travel through Hundred-Acre Wood in an oversized Hunny Pot and get lost in the pages of A.A. Milne’s classic tales.

name: Under the Sea - Journey of the Little Mermaid
Description: Board a clamshell and become part of Ariel’s world on a musical adventure awash with scenes from the animated classic.

name: Big Thunder Mountain Railroad
Description: Race through a haunted gold mine aboard a speeding train on this thrilling coaster-style ride.

name: The Haunted Mansion
Description: Climb aboard a gloomy Doom Buggy for a grave journey through a labyrinth of haunted chambers.

name: See Mickey at Town Square Theater
Description: Go backstage as a special guest of your pal, Mickey Mouse.

name: Astro Orbiter
Description: Pilot a spaceship high in the sky amid a gleaming constellation of planets.

name: Buzz Lightyear's Space Ranger Spin
Description: Fire your laser to earn points and defeat the Evil Emperor Zurg as you journey through a galactic space battle.

name: Monsters, Inc. Laugh Floor
Description: Participate in a hilarious, gag-tastic interactive comedy show—starring Monsters, Inc. and company!

name: Space Mountain
Description: Blast off on a rip-roaring rocket into the furthest reaches of outer space on this roller-coaster ride in the dark.

name: Tomorrowland Speedway
Description: Put the pedal to the metal in your very own hotrod and cruise along a scenic miniature motorway.

name: Tomorrowland Transit Authority PeopleMover
Description: Embark on a 10-minute tour of Tomorrowland aboard this mass transit system of the future.
